                children: "I made a promise to my friend, Bobby. If he could get just one new user to sign up by the end of the week, I pledged to write a blog about his startup journey with Pear[^1]. Thirty minutes later, after a quick trip to Subway and back, two new emails had landed in his database (I'm not great with bets...). Now, as I sit here typing, I'm dedicating my very first blog to him."
